---
import { site } from "../content/site";
import { img } from "../content/images";
---

<section
  id="despre"
  class="section bg-[var(--color-surface-container-low)]"
>
  <div class="container-page grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center">
    <div class="reveal order-2 md:order-1">
      <div
        class="aspect-[4/5] w-full max-w-md mx-auto md:mx-0 rounded-[1rem] overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-surface-container)]"
      >
        <img
          src={img("ana-portrait")}
          alt="Portret al Anei"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          width="800"
          height="1000"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal order-1 md:order-2">
      <h2 class="heading-lg">Bună, sunt Ana</h2>
      <span class="gold-divider"></span>

      <div
        class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] leading-relaxed"
      >
        <p>
          Am început manichiura lucrând pentru prietene și familie, iar de
          câțiva ani o fac cu seriozitate, pentru tot mai multe cliente. Pun
          suflet în fiecare set de unghii și știu că pot livra un rezultat de
          care să fii mulțumită.
        </p>
        <p>
          Lucrez cu produse de calitate, în condiții de igienă atente, și îmi
          place să ascult ce își dorește fiecare clientă, ca rezultatul să fie
          exact pe gustul tău.
        </p>
        <p>
          Dacă vrei unghii îngrijite și un moment doar pentru tine, te aștept în
          Iezureni.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Signature sign-off: the page's warmest moment, signed in Ana's own
           hand. Uses the italic Fraunces wordmark face (the brand mark) + the
           gold accent, so it reads as a personal signature, not a label. -->
      <p
        class="signature mt-6 text-[var(--color-primary)]"
        aria-label="semnat, Ana"
      >
        <span aria-hidden="true">cu drag, Ana</span>
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-sm">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="heading-md text-[var(--color-on-surface)]">
            {site.stats.years}
          </p>
          <p class="label-md uppercase text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] mt-1">
            ani de experiență
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="heading-md text-[var(--color-on-surface)]">1&nbsp;la&nbsp;1</p>
          <p class="label-md uppercase text-[var(--color-on-surface-variant)] mt-1">
            doar tu și Ana
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* The sign-off, in the italic Fraunces wordmark face — the brand's own
     signature hand. A short gold rule grows in beneath it once the section
     reveals, like the flourish under a handwritten name. The underline is
     decorative only; the readable text carries the meaning. */
  .signature {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-optical-sizing: auto;
    font-variation-settings: "SOFT" 40, "opsz" 40;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .signature span {
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 0.35rem;
    background-image: linear-gradient(var(--color-gold), var(--color-gold));
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: 0 100%;
    /* Default (no-JS, crawlers): the flourish is fully drawn. Mirrors the
       .reveal contract — never gate visible content on the animation. */
    background-size: 100% 1.5px;
  }

  /* Only when JS enables the reveal system do we start the rule hidden and
     draw it in once the About block scrolls into view. */
  :global(.js-reveal) .signature span {
    background-size: 0% 1.5px;
    transition: background-size 900ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 250ms;
  }

  :global(.js-reveal) .reveal.is-visible .signature span {
    background-size: 100% 1.5px;
  }

  /* Failsafe force-reveal and reduced-motion both snap to the drawn rule with
     no animation — consistent with the global reveal behaviour. */
  :global(.js-reveal) .reveal.reveal-now .signature span {
    transition: none;
    background-size: 100% 1.5px;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    :global(.js-reveal) .signature span {
      transition: none;
      background-size: 100% 1.5px;
    }
  }
</style>
